\c 1
\s Ukuthotshiswa kukaEdoma
\p
\v 1 Umbono kaObhadiya. Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova mayelana leEdoma\x + Hez. 25.12; 35.2; Jow. 3.19.\x*: Sizwile umbiko ovela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, njalo kuthunywe isithunywa phakathi kwezizwe\x + Mika 5.5; Gen. 1.26.\x*\x + 1.4; Jer. 49.14-16.\x*: Sukumani, kasimvukele empini!
\v 2 Khangela, ngikwenze waba mncinyane phakathi kwezizwe\x + 1.3.\x*, udelelwe kakhulu\x + 1.4; Jer. 49.14-16.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Ukuziqhenya kwenhliziyo yakho\x + 1.4; Jer. 49.14-16.\x* kukukhohlisile, \add wena\add* ohlala ezingoxweni zamadwala\x + 1.3.\x*, ondawo yakhe yokuhlala iphakeme\x + Amos 6.3.\x*, othi enhliziyweni yakhe: Ngubani ozangehlisela emhlabathini\x + Isa. 14.13; Isam. 18.7.\x*?
\v 4 Loba uphakeme njengokhozi\x + 1.4; Jer. 49.14-16.\x*\x + Isa. 14.13; Isam. 18.7.\x*, njalo loba ubeka isidleke sakho phakathi kwezinkanyezi\x + Isa. 14.13; Isam. 18.7.\x*\x + Jobe 20.6; Hab. 2.9.\x*\x + Amos 9.2.\x*, ngizakwethula khona, itsho iN\nd kosi\x + Amos 9.2.\x*\nd*.
\v 5 Uba amasela efika kuwe, loba abaphangi ebusuku\x + Jer. 49.9.\x* (uqunywe kangakanani!\x + Isa. 6.5.\x*) bebengayikuntshontsha baze banele yini? Uba abavuni bezithelo zevini bebengafika kuwe\x + Jer. 49.9.\x*, bebengayikutshiya umkhothozo yini\x + Isa. 17.6; Dute. 24.21.\x*?
\v 6 Yeka ukuhlolwa kwe\add zinto zika\add*Esawu\x + Jer. 49.10.\x*, ukudingisiswa kokuligugu kwakhe okufihliweyo!
\v 7 Wonke amadoda esivumelwano sakho akuthumele emngceleni; amadoda okuthula kwakho akukhohlisile, akwehlule\x + 1.3.\x*, \add adla\add* isinkwa sakho abeke\x + Hlab. 41.9.\x* imbule ngaphansi kwakho\x + Jer. 30.13; Hos. 5.13.\x*; kakukho ukuqedisisa kuye\x + Jer. 49.7.\x*.
\v 8 Kakuyikuba \add njalo\add* yini\x + Jobe 5.12,13.\x* ngalolosuku\x + Isa. 2.11.\x*, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuthi ngizachitha abahlakaniphileyo eEdoma lokuqedisisa\x + Jer. 49.7.\x* entabeni kaEsawu\x + 1.9,19,21; Hez. 35.2.\x*.
\v 9 Lamaqhawe akho\x + Hlab. 76.5; Amos 2.16.\x* azatshaywa luvalo, Themani\x + Jer. 49.7.\x*\x + Amos 1.12; 1 Lan. 1.45.\x*, ukuze ngulowo lalowo aqunywe entabeni kaEsawu ngokubulawa\x + 1.9,19,21; Hez. 35.2.\x*.
