\v 10 Ngenxa\x + Hlab. 137.7; Jer. 12.14; Lilo 4.21,22; Hez. 35.5; Amos 1.11.\x* yodlakela lwakho umelene\x + Zaga 10.6.\x* lomfowenu uJakobe\x + Gen. 27.41; Dute. 23.7.\x* inhloni zizakusibekela\x + Zaga 10.6.\x*, uqunywe kuze kube phakade\x + Hez. 35.9.\x*.
\v 11 Ngosuku owema ngalo uqondene \add labo\add*, ngosuku abezizweni abathumba ngalo amabutho akhe, abezizwe abangena emasangweni akhe\x + Hlab. 137.7; Jer. 12.14; Lilo 4.21,22; Hez. 35.5; Amos 1.11.\x*, abenza inkatho yokuphosa ngeJerusalema\x + Jow. 3.3.\x*, lawe wawunjengomunye wabo.
\v 12 Kodwa wawungafanelanga ukukhangela\x + Hlab. 22.17; Obad. 1.13; Mika 4.11; 7.10.\x* ngosuku lomfowenu\x + Hlab. 37.13.\x* ngosuku lwenhlupheko yakhe\x + Jobe 31.3.\x*; njalo wawungafanelanga uthokoze ngabantwana bakoJuda ngosuku lokuchitheka kwabo\x + Zaga 17.5; Mika 7.8.\x*; njalo wawungafanelanga ukhulume ngokuziqhenya ngosuku lokuhlupheka.
\v 13 Ngabe kawungenanga ngesango labantu bami osukwini lwenhlupheko yabo\x + Hez. 35.5.\x*; ngabe kawukhangelanga, lawe, ebubini babo osukwini lwenhlupheko yabo\x + Hlab. 22.17; Obad. 1.13; Mika 4.11; 7.10.\x*; njalo ngabe\x + Hez. 35.10.\x* kawelulelanga \add isandla sakho\add* enothweni yabo osukwini lwenhlupheko yabo\x + Eks. 22.8; 2 Sam. 6.6.\x*.
\v 14 Ngabe kawumanga emehlukanweni endlela ukuquma abaphunyukayo bakhe\x + Mat. 22.9; Hez. 21.21.\x*; njalo ngabe kawunikelanga abasalayo bakhe osukwini losizi\x + Jer. 42.17.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba usuku lweN\nd kosi\nd* lusondele\x + Jow. 2.1.\x*\x + Hez. 30.3; Jow. 3.14.\x* ezizweni zonke\x + Hez. 30.3; Jow. 3.14.\x*. Njengokwenza kwakho kuzakwenziwa kuwe\x + Jer. 50.29; Hez. 35.15; Hab. 2.8.\x*; umvuzo wakho uzabuyela ekhanda lakho\x + Jow. 3.4,7; Lilo 3.64.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba njengoba linathile\x + Jer. 25.28,29; 49.12; Nah. 3.11; Isam. 18.6; Jobe 21.20.\x* entabeni yami engcwele\x + Jow. 3.17.\x*, \add ngokunjalo\add* zonke izizwe zizanatha njalonjalo\x + Jer. 25.28,29; 49.12; Nah. 3.11; Isam. 18.6; Jobe 21.20.\x*, yebo, zizanatha, ziginye\x + Jer. 25.28,29; 49.12; Nah. 3.11; Isam. 18.6; Jobe 21.20.\x*, zibe kungathi kazizanga zibe khona\x + Jobe 10.19.\x*.
\s Ukuphakanyiswa kukaIsrayeli
\p
\v 17 Kodwa entabeni yeZiyoni\x + Jow. 2.32.\x* kuzakuba khona ukuphunyuka, kube lobungcwele\x + Jow. 2.32.\x*; lendlu kaJakobe izakudla ilifa lamafa ayo\x + Amos 9.8.\x*\x + Hez. 36.12.\x*.
\v 18 Lendlu kaJakobe izakuba ngumlilo\x + Isa. 10.17; Jer. 5.14; Zek. 12.6.\x*, lendlu kaJosefa ibe lilangabi\x + Isa. 10.17; Jer. 5.14; Zek. 12.6.\x*, lendlu kaEsawu ibe libibi\x + Jow. 2.5.\x*; njalo bazazitshisa\x + Hlab. 7.13.\x* bazidle\x + Isa. 10.17; Jer. 5.14; Zek. 12.6.\x*; njalo kakuyikuba khona oseleyo endlini kaEsawu\x + Hez. 25.14.\x*; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulumile.
