\v 19 Labeningizimu\x + Josh. 10.40; Hlu. 1.9; Jer. 17.26.\x* bazakudla ilifa\x + Amos 9.12.\x* lentaba kaEsawu\x + 1.8.\x*, lalabo\x + Zef. 2.5-7.\x* abemagcekeni amaFilisti\x + Josh. 10.40; Hlu. 1.9; Jer. 17.26.\x*, yebo bazakudla ilifa lensimu yakoEfrayimi lensimu yeSamariya\x + Jer. 23.13.\x*, loBhenjamini iGileyadi.
\v 20 Labathunjiweyo bale inqaba yabantwana bakoIsrayeli \add bazakudla ilifa\add* elalingelamaKhanani\x + Amos 9.12.\x*, kuze kufike eZarefathi\x + 1 Kho. 17.9,10; Luka 4.26.\x*; labathunjiweyo beJerusalema abaseSefaredi bazakudla ilifa lemizi yeningizimu\x + Josh. 10.40; Hlu. 1.9; Jer. 17.26.\x*.
